}

desc: "hestia is an open source hosting control panel. hestia has a clean and focused interface without the clutter. hestia has the latest of very innovative technologies. hestia is a fork from VestaCP, special thanks to vestacp.com and Serghey Rodin. This package provides the custom compiled PHP-FPM backend for Hestia Control Panel."